{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"contains","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/contains","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath 참고 문서</a></b>: <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 요소</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 함수</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 축</a>\n</div><p></p>\n<p><br>\n <code>contains</code> 함수는 첫 번째 인수 문자열이 두 번째 인수 문자열을 포함하는지 결정하고 부울값 true 또는 false를 반환합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.ac.b8.eb.b2.95","title":"문법","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">contains(<i>haystack</i> ,<i>needle</i> )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.9d.b8.ec.88.98","title":"인수","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect2\">\n  <code>\n  <i>\n   haystack</i>\n  </code></dt>\n <dd>\n  찾을 문자열</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect3\">\n  <code>\n  <i>\n   needle</i>\n  </code></dt>\n <dd>\n  첫 번째 인수(<code>\n  <i>\n   haystack</i>\n  </code>)에서 찾을 부분 문자열</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.b0.98.ed.99.98","title":"반환","isH3":true,"content":"<p>첫 번째 인수(<code>\n <i>\n  haystack</i>\n </code>)가 두 번째 인수(<code>\n <i>\n  needle</i>\n </code>)를 포함하면 <code>true</code>. 그렇지 않으면, <code>false</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a0.95.ec.9d.98","title":"정의","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-contains\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.2</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_.ec.a7.80.ec.9b.90","title":"Gecko 지원","isH3":true,"content":"<p>지원함.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"contains 함수는 첫 번째 인수 문자열이 두 번째 인수 문자열을 포함하는지 결정하고 부울값 true 또는 false를 반환합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"contains","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"contains","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"contains","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"contains","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"contains","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/xpath/functions/contains","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/xpath/functions/contains/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/contains","title":"contains"}],"pageTitle":"contains - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}